      "content": "it just feels so heavy sometimes. i look at them and think, wouldn't they be so much freer if they didn't have to worry about me anymore? if i just... wasn't an issue they had to solve every single day. it feels like the most selfless thing would be to just stop being a problem for them. do you think that's crazy?",
